 I need to improve my love life.
I spent all the night working. I had to clean the floor and the tables and <strike>try not to get molested by the boss</strike>. *yawn* At least, I've got free time this week-end.

Hi! Mazaki Anzu here~ (just call me Anzu, 'kay?). Today, Mom asked me again if I was ever planning to quit my job at Burger World. No Mommy, I'll keep working there 'til I die or 'til I finally own this goddamned place! Mwahahahaha! No, I didn't tell her that in fact. I just said: "I don't know, Mom." I don't really want her to know about my not-so-secret ambition about becoming the big boss of a fast-food restaurant. Why does she want me to quit? This job's quite well-paid, I've working there for two years, the uniforms are great and the boss just loves my breasts me. Burger World is my life (first person saying I have no life will get some extra super-strong-mustard on their burger).
